$h2 Migration from Play! Framework 2.6.x to 2.7.x

$h3 Maven-related changes

a) change Play! version from

```
    <properties>
        ...
        <play2.version>${play26LatestVersion}</play2.version>
    </properties>
```

to

```
    <properties>
        ...
        <play2.version>${play27LatestVersion}</play2.version>
    </properties>
```

b) if using Ebean, upgrade `play-ebean` dependency version to `5.0.0-M2`
